The module TeX-tools contains the following set of files:


colorPPR.tex            macro.tex
PPRVincent.sty          cover-Template.tex      notation.gdf
macro-Slide.tex         ntheorem.sty
acronym.gdf             macro-SlidePPR.tex      package-Slide.tex
doc25pdf.sh


This set of files ensures the use of common variables for the SICONOS TeX Files in order to improve the homogeneity. To use it, add the directory TeX-tools in your environment variable TEXINPUTS like that (csh style):

setenv TEXINPUTS  .:/usr/share/texmf::/Path/To/TeX-tools:
